        '<sub><math><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi><mi>max</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mi>ωA</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>100</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt><mspace width="0.08em"/><mi>cm</mi><mo>/</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mo>→</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mo>.</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>100</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt><mo>→</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>10</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt><mspace width="0.08em"/><mi>cm</mi></math></sub> <sub><math><mtable columnalign="left"><mtr><mtd><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup><mo>+</mo><msubsup><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mn>2</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mtext>cos</mtext><mfenced close=")" open="(" separators=""><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">φ</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">φ</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfenced><mo>→</mo><msup><mfenced close=")" open="(" separators=""><mn>10</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt></mfenced><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></msubsup><mo>+</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>.</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>.</mo><mtext>cos</mtext><mfenced close=")" open="(" separators=""><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">π</mi><mn>6</mn></mfrac><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">π</mi></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac></mfenced></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mo>→</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>10</mn><mspace width="0.08em"/><mi>cm</mi><mo>.</mo></mtd></mtr></mtable></math></sub><img src="https://apiemsdev.hocmai.net/resource/uploads/image/e1bd9b2e-9976-4ecb-8d0b-5cb11c7a1de2.emf.svg" />Gọi <math><mi>H</mi></math> là trung điểm <math><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></math><math><mo>⇒</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>H</mi><mo>⊥</mo><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></math>.Ta có: <math><mfenced close="}" open="" separators=""><mtable columnalign="left"><mtr><mtd><mi>A</mi><msup><mi>A</mi><mo>′</mo></msup><mo>⊥</mo><mfenced close=")" open="(" separators=""><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mfenced></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi><mo>⊂</mo><mfenced close=")" open="(" separators=""><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mfenced></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced></math><math><mo>⇒</mo><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi><mo>⊥</mo><mi>A</mi><msup><mi>A</mi><mo>′</mo></msup></math><math><mo>⇒</mo></math> Góc giữa <math><mfenced close=")" open="(" separators=""><msup><mi>A</mi><mo>′</mo></msup><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mfenced></math>và <math><mfenced close=")" open="(" separators=""><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mfenced></math> là <math><mn>30</mn><mo>°</mo></math>.Gọi <math><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi></math>, theo bài ra ta có:<math><mfenced close="" open="{" separators=""><mtable columnalign="left"><mtr><mtd><mi>A</mi><mi>H</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mi>A</mi><msup><mi>A</mi><mo>′</mo></msup><mo>=</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>H</mi><mo>.</mo><mi>tan30</mi><mo>°</mo><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced></math> <math><mo>⇒</mo><msup><mi>A</mi><mo>′</mo></msup><mi>H</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mi>A</mi><msup><msup><mi>A</mi><mo>′</mo></msup><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>A</mi><msup><mi>H</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi></math>.Mà <math><msub><mi>S</mi><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><msup><mi>A</mi><mo>′</mo></msup><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math><math><mo>⇔</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi><mo>.</mo><msup><mi>A</mi><mo>′</mo></msup><mi>H</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math><math><mo>⇔</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>.</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>.</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math><math><mo>⇒</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>a</mi><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt></math>.Vậy thể tích cần tìm là <math><mi>V</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>S</mi><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow></msub><mo>.</mo><mi>A</mi><msup><mi>A</mi><mo>′</mo></msup></math><math><mo>=</mo><mfenced close=")" open="(" separators=""><msup><mfenced close=")" open="(" separators=""><mn>2</mn><mi>a</mi><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt></mfenced><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>.</mo><mfrac><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mfenced><mo>.</mo><mi>a</mi><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><msqrt><mn>6</mn></msqrt></math>.',
