      level: 1,
      type: 0,
      awareness_level: 1,
      answer_type: 0,
      solution:
        'Ta có <math><mi>S</mi><mi>A</mi><mo>⊥</mo><mfenced close=")" open="(" separators=""><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mfenced></math> nên <em>AC</em> là hình chiếu của <em>SC</em> lên mặt phẳng <math><mfenced close=")" open="(" separators=""><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mfenced><mo>.</mo></math> Do đó <math><mfenced close=")" open="(" separators=""><mi>S</mi><mi>C</mi><mn>,</mn><mfenced close=")" open="(" separators=""><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mfenced></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfenced close=")" open="(" separators=""><mi>S</mi><mi>C</mi><mn>,</mn><mi>A</mi><mi>C</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mover accent="true"><mrow><mi>S</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mo stretchy="true">^</mo></mover><mo>.</mo></math> Tam giác <em>ABC</em> vuông tại <em>B</em> có <math><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>a</mi><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt></math> và <math><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>a</mi></math> nên <math><mi>A</mi><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mi>A</mi><msup><mi>B</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>B</mi><msup><mi>C</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>4</mn><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>a</mi><mo>.</mo></math> Do đó tam giác <em>SAC</em> vuông cân tại <em>A</em> nên <math><mover accent="true"><mrow><mi>S</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mo stretchy="true">^</mo></mover><mo>=</mo><mn>45</mn><mo>°</mo><mo>.</mo></math> Vậy <math><mfenced close=")" open="(" separators=""><mi>S</mi><mi>C</mi><mn>,</mn><mfenced close=")" open="(" separators=""><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mfenced></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mn>45</mn><mo>°</mo><mo>.</mo></math>',
